queryParameters.description:
The type of option, which determines how it will display on the storefront. Acceptable values: 
C: Checkbox; 
D: Date field; 
F: File upload field;
MT: Multi-line text field; 
RB: Radio buttons;
RT: Rectangular boxes (for product sizes);
S: Select/drop-down list;
C: Numbers-only text field; 
P: Product Pick list; 
CS: Color/texture Swatch; 
T: Text field.
